#Articles
All the files inside gh-pages/docs/_posts are licensed under
CC BY 4.0. The attribution requirement is only met when:

The canonical link is directed towards the original article, e.g.
<link rel="canonical" href="https://www.anupamchugh.github.io/ugly-truths-about-working-from-home.html" />

The following message is displayed above and below the article:
This article has been originally published on <a href="https://www.anupamchugh.github.io/">Anupam Chugh's website</a>.


